"title": "8720: double-mindedness",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8720: double-mindedness",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Indicative of insincerity and hypocrisy. God requires wholeheartedness and sincerity from all people, both in their dealings with others and in their worship of him.</p>\n<h2>Double-mindedness is characteristic of sinners</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:8\">JAS 4:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:113-Ps119:115\">PSA 119:113–119:115</a></p>\n<h2>Double-mindedness in dealings with other people</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen34:1-Gen34:29\">GEN 34:1–34:29</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh9:3-Josh9:15\">JOS 9:3–9:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam18:17-1Sam18:25\">1SA 18:17–18:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:22-2Sam3:27\">2SA 3:22–3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:8-2Sam20:10\">2SA 20:8–20:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:1-Neh6:4\">NEH 6:1–6:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh6:10-Neh6:13\">NEH 6:10–6:13</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:47-Matt26:50\">MAT 26:47–26:50</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:43-Mark14:46\">MRK 14:43–14:46</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:47-Luke22:48\">LUK 22:47–22:48</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts23:12-Acts23:24\">ACT 23:12–23:24</a></p>\n<h2>Double-mindedness in daily life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:25-Matt23:28\">MAT 23:25–23:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:10-Matt15:19\">MAT 15:10–15:19</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:14-Mark7:23\">MRK 7:14–7:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:39-Luke11:40\">LUK 11:39–11:40</a></p>\n<h2>Double-mindedness in worship</h2>\n<h3>Idolatry</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:21\">1KI 18:21</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:27-2Kgs17:34\">2KI 17:27–17:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:40-2Kgs17:41\">2KI 17:40–17:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos10:1-Hos10:2\">HOS 10:1–10:2</a></p>\n<h3>Insincerity</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:1-Matt15:9\">MAT 15:1–15:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:1-Mark7:13\">MRK 7:1–7:13</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a></p>\n<h2>Lack of faith in prayer is equated with double-mindedness</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas1:5-Jas1:8\">JAS 1:5–1:8</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God requires wholeheartedness and sincerity</h2>\n<h3>Towards himself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:20-Num14:24\">NUM 14:20–14:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh14:14\">JOS 14:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:21\">2CH 31:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:9\">ROM 12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor5:8\">1CO 5:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:12\">2CO 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:8\">1TI 3:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas3:13-Jas3:17\">JAS 3:13–3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Towards other people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:22\">COL 3:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:8-2Chr19:11\">2CH 19:8–19:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph6:5-Eph6:9\">EPH 6:5–6:9</a></p>",
